com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.dynamictype
Interface DynamictypePackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
DynamictypePackage
public static interface DynamictypePackage.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
